    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to list this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it just left the showroom! I've kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it since day one, so it\u2019s looking spotless and ready for a new adventure. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new and drives like a dream, you really have to see this one in person. Shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
